desc: No more tan lines! Australia’s first tan thru swimwear that allows the suns rays to penetrate the fabric, giving you an all over natural tan. Free shipping on all orders!

layout.text: ENJOY AN AMAZING, NATURAL, ALL OVER TAN!

We developed a revolutionary fabric that lets the sun shine safely through, to help give you a natural all over tan.
Let the sun shine! And say goodbye to unsightly tan lines.
